short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Rule-Based phishing attack detector for Online-Banking web sites

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A powerful extension to detect phishing attacks in Online-Banking web sites. It is a rule-based system that analyses the webpage content to identify phishing attacks. PhishDetector has the ability to detect online-banking phishing scams quickly with zero false negative alarm. For accurate result, it is recommended to use this extension for your Online-Banking web pages only.
